<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Login Alert</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #f39c12; color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .details { background: #fff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #f39c12; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #e74c3c; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>ðŸ”“ New Login Detected</h1>
        <p>Account access notification</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{firstName}} {{lastName}},</h2>
        
        <p>We detected a new login to your {{appName}} account. Here are the details:</p>
        
        <div class="details">
            <h3>Login Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</p>
            <p><strong>Device:</strong> {{device}}</p>
            <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{timestamp}}</p>
            <p><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ipAddress}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>If this was you, no action is needed. This notification is just to keep you informed about your account activity.</p>
        
        <p><strong>However, if this wasn't you:</strong></p>
        <ol>
            <li>Change your password immediately</li>
            <li>Review your authorized devices</li>
            <li>Enable two-factor authentication</li>
            <li>Contact our support team</li>
        </ol>
        
        <a href="{{appUrl}}/account/security" class="button">Review Account Security</a>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The {{appName}} Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>{{appName}} | <a href="{{appUrl}}">{{appUrl}}</a></p>
        <p>This is an automated security notification.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>